flowchart TD
    A[Admin signs in with workforce Entra] --> B[AdminEntra validates token]
    B --> C[Resolve local UserAccount]
    C --> D[Load scopes and permissions]
    D --> E{Provision foreign e-Service user?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Validate existing Person and Student]
    F --> G[Create IdentityProvisioningRequest]
    G --> H[Call Entra External ID through Graph adapter]
    H --> I{Provider result}
    I -->|Success| J[Create local UserAccount mapping]
    I -->|Uncertain timeout| K[Search provider before retry]
    I -->|Failure| L[Mark failed and expose safe support status]
    J --> M[User signs in with Entra External ID]
    M --> N[Validate external token]
    N --> O[Resolve local UserAccount and Person]
    O --> P[Activate first login]
    P --> Q[e-Service access]

    R[Singapore citizen selects Singpass] --> S[MockPass locally or Singpass externally]
    S --> T[Validate callback/token]
    T --> U[Match PersonIdentifier]
    U --> V[Resolve or create local Singpass mapping]
    V --> W[Check Student or Account Holder eligibility]
    W --> Q
